\mathbb{P}[X\leq k]\geq \mathbb{P}[\text{Bin}(n,p)\leq k]
X=\sum\limits_{i=1}^n \mathbf{1}_{U_i<p_i}\quad\text{and}\quad  \text{Bin}(n,p) = \sum\limits_{i=1}^n \mathbf{1}_{U_i<p}
 X\leq \text{Bin}(n,p)
\{\text{Bin}(n,p)\leq k\}\subset \{X\leq k\}
